<br>
Once you get this attitude and find a few like minded souls there can be some great RP here.  In fact, right now, I am participating in the most in depth and involved RP of my gaming life. (Thats 20 years, man and boy, youngster).<br>
<br>
To me people with the RP police attitude will find any environment which deals with more than a closed group of about 6 people impossible to get along in.  You can only enjoy these worlds once you accept that no-one else shares exactly your view of how things should work, and you RP around that. <p>Lord Regent <b>Gray Hateborn</b><br>
